Test designs for Sayma boards (ddr3, drtio, amc-rtm link, jesd204b)

[> Status
---------
- ddr3: 32 bit and 64 bit ddr3 validated at 1Gbps/pin.
- drtio: MultiGTH validated with 2 lanes at 1.25Gbps.
- amc-rtm link: artix7 and ultrascale low level loopback validated at 1.25Gbps, need testing with AMC/RTM.
- jesd204b: untested
